<https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/11946>
    dc:description "Figure 94 - 95. 94 Prasmodon zlotnicki. Body, dorsal view 95 Prasmodon eminens. Body, dorsal view." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/11946" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/11937>
    dc:description "Figures 40 - 45. Prasmodon masoni. 40 Habitus 41 Fore wing 42 Head and mesosoma (partially), lateral view 43 Hypopygium, ovipositor, ovipositor sheaths, and hind leg (partially), lateral view 44 Head and mesosoma, dorsal view 45 Propodeum and metasoma, dorsal view." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/11937" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/11952>
    dc:description "Figure 105. Neighbor-Joining tree (Saitou and Nei 1987) based on distances computed using the Kimura 2 - parameter method (Kimura 1980) of all Prasmodon sequences from the ACG. Tree tips are labeled with species name | specimen accession | host information | sequence length and  ambiguities | type status." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/11952" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

